OL,3,CGovernment facing backlash over prison
OL,4,Crecall changes to free up jail space
OL,6,FMinisters are facing a backlash from
OL,7,Fvictims and domestic abuse watchdogs
OL,8,Fover planned changes to prison recall
OL,9,Fwhich would see some offenders
OL,10,Freleased within a month to free up
OL,11,Fjail space.
OL,13,FUnder emergency measures announced by
OL,14,Fthe Justice Secretary, some criminals
OL,15,Fserving sentences between one and four
OL,16,Fyears will be returned to custody only
OL,17,Ffor a fixed 28-day period.
