OL,3,CGovernment facing backlash over prison
OL,4,Crecall changes to free up jail space
OL,6,FOffenders are recalled to prison if
OL,7,Fthey commit another offence or breach
OL,8,Flicence conditions, such as by missing
OL,9,Fprobation appointments, when they are
OL,10,Freleased early but remain on licence.
OL,12,FShabana Mahmood said the changes were
OL,13,Fnecessary to curb overcrowding as she
OL,14,Fwarned jails are on track to be down
OL,15,Fto "zero capacity" by November.
OL,17,FThe plans were criticised by victims
OL,18,Fcommissioner Baroness Newlove and
OL,19,Fdomestic abuse commissioner Dame
OL,20,FNicole Jacobs, who said lives would be
OL,21,Fin danger as a result of the decision.
