OL,6,FBaroness Newlove said: "Victims will
OL,7,Funderstandably feel unnerved and
OL,8,Fbewildered by today's announcement.
OL,10,F"If the Probation Service, the
OL,11,Fsecretary of state and the Parole
OL,12,FBoard have all judged these
OL,13,Findividuals to pose a risk of harm to
OL,14,Fthe public, then reducing time served
OL,15,Fon recall can only place victims and
OL,16,Fthe wider public at an unnecessary
OL,17,Frisk of harm."
