OL,6,FDame Nicole called for the proposal to
OL,7,Fbe scrapped, saying: "I cannot stress
OL,8,F(enough) the lack of consideration for
OL,9,Fvictims' safety and how many lives are
OL,10,Fbeing put in danger because of this
OL,11,Fproposed change.
OL,13,F"You are not sent to prison for four
OL,14,Fyears if you do not pose significant
OL,15,Frisk to your victim or the wider
OL,16,Fpublic.
OL,18,F"Re-releasing them back into the
OL,19,Fcommunity after 28 days is simply
OL,20,Funacceptable."
