OL,3,CGovernment facing backlash over prison
OL,4,Crecall changes to free up jail space
OL,6,FShadow justice secretary Robert
OL,7,FJenrick said Labour was "making the
OL,8,Fproblem worse".
OL,10,FHe said: "Under Labour's new rules,
OL,11,Finstead of being recalled to serve the
OL,12,Frest of their sentence, they'll be
OL,13,Fgiven a fixed-term recall of a pitiful
OL,14,F28 days.
OL,16,F"They are then released, with no
OL,17,Freassessment of risk or Parole Board
OL,18,Foversight.
OL,20,F"That is not justice. It's a recipe
OL,21,Ffor the breakdown of law and order.
