OL,3,CGovernment facing backlash over prison
OL,4,Crecall changes to free up jail space
OL,6,F"By telling prisoners that they will
OL,7,Fnever serve their full sentence, even
OL,8,Fif they reoffend, the Justice
OL,9,FSecretary has removed an important
OL,10,Fdeterrent."
OL,12,FAndrea Coomber KC, chief executive of
OL,13,Fcharity the Howard League for Penal
OL,14,FReform, said the recall change is a
OL,15,F"logical step to take" when the recall
OL,16,Fpopulation is rising so quickly, and
OL,17,Fsaid the upcoming sentencing review is
OL,18,Fa chance for "a lasting solution to
OL,19,Fthis mess".
