OL,3,CGovernment facing backlash over prison
OL,4,Crecall changes to free up jail space
OL,6,F"There is no time to lose, and only
OL,7,Fbold reform will do," she said.
OL,9,FMinisters say the scheme will exclude
OL,10,Fpeople convicted of serious violent or
OL,11,Fsexual offences, as well as terrorist
OL,12,Fand national security crimes.
OL,14,FThe exclusions will focus on offenders
OL,15,Fmanaged under Multi-Agency Public
OL,16,FProtection Arrangements (Mappa) at
OL,17,FLevel 2 or 3, the PA news agency
OL,18,Funderstands.
