OL,6,FMappa is used to manage certain sexual
OL,7,Fand violent offenders in the
OL,8,Fcommunity, with only the most complex
OL,9,For high-risk individuals put at Level
OL,10,F2 or 3.
OL,12,FIt is hoped the emergency measures
OL,13,Fwill free up 1,400 prison places and
OL,14,F"buy time" before sentencing reforms
OL,15,Fexpected to come into force next
OL,16,Fspring.
OL,18,FLegislation to bring in the changes is
OL,19,Fexpected to be introduced in the
OL,20,Fcoming weeks.
