OL,6,FMs Mahmood also announced three new
OL,7,Fprisons will be built, starting this
OL,8,Fyear, as part of a "record prison
OL,9,Fexpansion", but admitted "we cannot
OL,10,Fbuild our way out of this crisis".
OL,12,F"The consequences of failing to act
OL,13,Fare unthinkable, but they must be
OL,14,Funderstood," she said.
OL,16,F"If our prisons overflow, courts
OL,17,Fcancel trials, police halt their
OL,18,Farrests, crime goes unpunished and we
OL,19,Freach a total breakdown of law and
OL,20,Forder."
